checkers.javari.quals

Annotation Type ThisMutable


  • @TypeQualifier
 @Target(value={})
 @SubtypeOf(value=ReadOnly.class)
public @interface ThisMutable
    An annotation used to represent a place holder immutability type, that is equivalent to the ThisMutable type in the Javari typesystem.

    This annotation may not be written in source code; it is an implementation detail of the checker.
